'''Sean Llewellyn Williams''' is an author, writer of [[Star Wars: The Force Unleashed (novelization)|''The Force Unleashed'']] novel and co-writer of three [[Star Wars: The New Jedi Order|''New Jedi Order'']] novels with [[Shane Dix]].

Williams wrote a [[canon]] short story titled “[[Impact (short story)|Impact]],” which was published in the anthology book ''[[From a Certain Point of View: Return of the Jedi]]''.

